text: K M Abdul Khaleq Chontu is a Bangladesh Nationalist Party politician and the former Member of Parliament of Kushtia-3. ==Career== Chontu was elected to parliament from Kushtia-3 as a Bangladesh Nationalist Party candidate in 1991. ==References== Category:Bangladesh Nationalist Party politicians Category:Living people Category:5th Jatiya Sangsad members Category:Year of birth missing (living people)
title: K M Abdul Khaleq Chontu
